| 
| An enumeration of three values that may commonly occur in constraint models.
| 
| Use as the type of any attribute within this model, which expresses constraint on some
| attribute in a class in a reference model. For example to indicate validity of Date/Time
| fields.
| 

enum VALIDITY_KIND
    base_type String

        mandatory (mandatory)

        optional (optional)

        prohibited (prohibited)

        disallowed (disallowed)


end
